<paragraph id="E59B2A68E058A24B64D1975483CD986F" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Known from the</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5C2363010622CED38D3BD65AA8863354" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" type="type locality">
<paragraph id="7FF50FE92B6EAA241AFE75E75FFDA5AD" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="06BC0FB2C35D08E812D314554F7B99E8" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
and 3 other locations further south on the French Atlantic coast (
<bibRefCitation id="CEDC4DF8E8C9809E47194C61550B0C0D" author="Lagardere, J-P" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin du Centre d'Etudes et des Recherches Scientifiques Biarritz" pageId="7" pageNumber="140" pagination="143 - 209" title="Recherche sur la biologie et l'ecologie de la macrofaune des substrats meubles de la cote des landes et de la cote Basque." volume="6" year="1966">Lagardere 1966</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5E40C2EA73513E868DA6D885819D6F92" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" type="epidermal pigment patterns">
