<paragraph id="8A41534A8CF44AF5A49BB3745FE55156" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
Remarks The largest species of 
<taxonomicName id="4932D59CEFD9368A15F29A6974202E5E" class="Malacostraca" family="Talitridae" genus="Macarorchestia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Macarorchestia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Macarorchestia</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
